  "body": "I've noticed that our metrics do not include any blob_transaction db size information.\r\nCurrent size for goerli after Dencun:\r\n```\r\n59G\t    ./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli/state\r\n45G\t    ./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli/receipts\r\n256G\t./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli/blocks\r\n8.9G\t./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli/code\r\n4.0K\t./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli/peers\r\n4.1M\t./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli/witness\r\n461M\t./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli/blockInfos\r\n550M\t./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli/blockNumbers\r\n4.1M\t./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli/badBlocks\r\n2.7G\t./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli/bloom\r\n3.4G\t./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli/headers\r\n4.1M\t./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli/canonicalHashTrie\r\n4.2M\t./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli/metadata\r\n1.8M\t./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli/discoveryNodes\r\n75M\t    ./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli/blobTransactions\r\n376G\t./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db/goerli\r\n376G\t./sedge-data/execution-data/nethermind_db\r\n```\r\n\r\nvs currently visible metrics in Grafana:\r\n```\r\nnethermind_cht_db_size\r\nnethermind_code_db_size\r\nnethermind_bloom_db_size\r\nnethermind_state_db_size\r\nnethermind_blocks_db_size\r\nnethermind_headers_db_size\r\nnethermind_witness_db_size\r\nnethermind_receipts_db_size\r\nnethermind_metadata_db_size\r\nnethermind_block_infos_db_size\r\n```\r\n\r\nSo I see missing:\r\n```\r\nblobTransactions\r\ndiscoveryNodes\r\nbadBlocks\r\nblockNumbers\r\npeers\r\n```\r\n\r\nAdditionally, I see that these metrics are reporting invalid data comparing to actual nethermind_Db content:\r\n- Receipts_db: In Goerli it is 45GB, metric shows 100KB\r\n- Metadata_db: in Goerli it is 4.2 MB, mertric shows 0\r\n- Witness_db: in Goerli it shows 4.1MB, metric shows 0\r\n- Bloom_db: in Goerli it is 2.7GB, metric shows 0\r\n- Canonical Hash Tree_db: in Goerli it shows 4.1MB, metric shows 0",
